overview_description.description: Kokobots specializes in the development and manufacturing of autonomous cleaning robots. With a focus on leveraging artificial intelligence, Kokobots offers a range of products including the Piolet S9, Discovery S95, and Pioneer series (S911, S975, S977). These robots are designed to perform cleaning tasks autonomously in various environments, utilizing Kokobots' proprietary AI OS and UniHPP Algorithm for efficient operation and navigation. The technology aims to provide solutions for intelligent cleaning in densely populated areas, equipped with full intelligence property autonomous cleaning control systems for autonomous navigation, obstacle avoidance, and task execution.
